OL,7,     Frequiring urgent attention and
OL,8,     Ftreatment; a 64-year-old stops
OL,9,     Fbreathing while her husband calls
OL,10,     Fthe hospital.
OL,11,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,12,     FDoctors treat a non-verbal young
OL,13,     Fman in a life-threatening
OL,14,     Fneurological emergency, while a
OL,15,     Fmidwife with severe spinal pain is
OL,16,     Ffeared to have cauda equina
OL,17,     Fsyndrome after back surgery.
