OL,5,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThe doctors of Hall Green Health
OL,7,     Fcome face to face with some rare
OL,8,     Fconditions. It's a reminder that
OL,9,     Fwhen you're a GP, you never know
